title: Malcolm Douglas - Australia - The Last Of A Tribe [1976]
description: Malcolm Douglas - 1x06 - The Last Of A Tribe - 1976 Adventure / Travel / Documentary https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malcolm_Douglas_(documentary_maker) Malcolm lives with the tribal elders of the Worora and Narinjin Tribes at their bush camp in the remote Kimberley. Daily he films activities of collecting food, hunting and ceremonial life. An important film showing a culture rapidly changing. When Malcolm Douglas immersed himself within an Indigenous cultural landscape, he took lounge rooms full of Australian viewers with him.
